        <abstract>
            <p>In addition to the drawing of a caterpillar which CD intends to use,</p> 
<p>HWB sends information on differences of colour and pattern between the sexes of species of <hi rend="italic">Papilio</hi>.</p>  
<p><hi rend="italic">Argynnis diana</hi> and <hi rend="italic">A. sagana</hi> have females that are brightly coloured, but these may be cases of protective mimicry.</p> 
        </abstract>
